description: This dashboard plots all the important metrics for Snowflake.
title: Snowflake Dashboard

deployment.environment.description: The deployment environment for the service.
deployment.environment.name: deployment.environment
deployment.environment.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT(JSONExtractString(labels, 'deployment.environment'))
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4
WHERE metric_name like '%snowflake%'

snowflake.account.name.name: snowflake.account.name
snowflake.account.name.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT(JSONExtractString(labels, 'snowflake.account.name'))
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4
WHERE metric_name like '%snowflake%'
